    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">23. Contact Us</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">For any questions, concerns, complaints, or requests regarding this Notice or how Savanna Hills Limited processes personal data through KiboAuto Marketplace, please contact us:</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-3"><strong>Savanna Hills Limited</strong><br>Trading as KiboAuto Marketplace<br>Website: <a href="https://kiboauto.co.tz" class="text-green-600 hover:underline">https://kiboauto.co.tz</a></p>
</section>
